    <item>
      <title>马斯克未能驳回前 Twitter 首席执行官的遣散费索赔请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/musk-loses-bid-to-dismiss-ex-twitter-ceo-s-severance-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 在 2022 年接管 Twitter 公司时解雇了多名高管，这些高管要求获得赔偿，但马斯克在一场法庭斗争中遭遇重大挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/musk-loses-bid-to-dismiss-ex-twitter-ceo-s-severance-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 04:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
