    <item>
      <title>声名狼藉的 Three Arrows 创始人妻子出售价值 3800 万美元的新加坡豪宅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/disgraced-three-arrows-founder-zhu-su-s-wife-sells-38-million-singapore-mansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[已破产的加密货币对冲基金三箭资本 (Three Arrows Capital) 联合创始人朱苏的妻子，尽管夫妻俩的其他一些资产被法院冻结，但仍成功以 5100 万新元（3850 万美元）的价格出售了她在新加坡拥有的一栋豪宅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-02/disgraced-three-arrows-founder-zhu-su-s-wife-sells-38-million-singapore-mansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2024 01:47:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>康卡斯特聘请摩根士丹利为潜在有线电视网络分拆提供咨询</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/comcast-taps-morgan-stanley-to-advise-on-cable-networks-spinoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，康卡斯特公司正在与投资银行摩根士丹利合作评估其有线电视网络的选择，此前该公司本周宣布正在考虑剥离有线电视业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/comcast-taps-morgan-stanley-to-advise-on-cable-networks-spinoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 22:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
