      <title>特斯拉出售 4.99 亿美元太阳能设备贷款支持债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/tesla-sells-499-million-of-debt-backed-by-solar-equipment-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司出售了价值 4.99 亿美元的债券，以向购买太阳能设备的客户提供贷款作为支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/tesla-sells-499-million-of-debt-backed-by-solar-equipment-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 20:32:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊隆·马斯克的 X 未能及时更新政治广告披露信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/elon-musk-s-x-falls-behind-on-updating-political-ad-disclosures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊隆马斯克的社交网络 X 在政治广告披露方面落后了，这让外界更难理解政客和政治行动委员会如何利用社交网络影响即将到来的选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/elon-musk-s-x-falls-behind-on-updating-political-ad-disclosures</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 20:22:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
